    "ci_benefits": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "settings": {
        "section_visibility": "always",
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"ci-feature-shell\">\n  <section class=\"ci-section\">\n    <div class=\"ci-wrap\">\n      <div class=\"ci-section-head\">\n        <p class=\"ci-kicker\">Benefits</p>\n        <h2>Why Choose Custom Over Universal</h2>\n        <p>A great universal can sound exceptional. A great custom sounds exceptional every single time you insert it. That is the difference — and it is felt long before it is measured.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"ci-benefit-grid\">\n        <div class=\"ci-benefit-card\">\n          <h3>A Fit That Belongs to You</h3>\n          <p>Because each shell is molded to your own ear, there are no pressure points, no hot spots, and no creeping discomfort. Your monitors stay where they were placed — through a two-hour set, a long-haul flight, or an afternoon of nothing but listening.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ci-benefit-card\">\n          <h3>Silence Without Batteries</h3>\n          <p>A full-shell custom blocks up to 26 dB of ambient noise. On stage, you can monitor at safer volumes. In a café, on a flight, in an open studio — you hear your music, the room around it falls away, and your hearing thanks you for it.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ci-benefit-card\">\n          <h3>Repeatable, Always</h3>\n          <p>With universals, every tip insertion is a small variable. With a custom, the driver sits at a fixed distance from your eardrum. Frequency response, imaging, soundstage — all identical, session after session. You stop tuning the fit and start trusting the sound.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ci-benefit-card\">\n          <h3>Designed for Hours</h3>\n          <p>Musicians wear our customs through three-hour performances without fatigue. The weight distributes across the concha, there are no tips pressing outward against the canal, and the shells warm to body temperature within minutes — invisible to the wearer.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ci-benefit-card\">\n          <h3>Built to Be Cherished</h3>\n          <p>Drivers can be replaced, sockets repaired, shells reshelled if your anatomy changes over the years. A well-maintained AAW custom can outlast a decade of daily listening — and in many cases, quietly, it does.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ci-benefit-card\">\n          <h3>An Object as Personal as the Sound</h3>\n          <p>Choose your shell color, your faceplate material, your artwork or engraving. From abalone and carbon fiber to deep solids and hand-painted details, every AAW custom comes with a faceplate consultation. The result is a monitor that looks as singular as it sounds.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n</div>",
