    "ci_why_aaw": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "settings": {
        "section_visibility": "always",
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"ci-feature-shell\">\n  <section class=\"ci-section\">\n    <div class=\"ci-wrap\">\n      <div class=\"ci-section-head\">\n        <p class=\"ci-kicker\">Why AAW</p>\n        <h2>Singapore Craft, Global Standard</h2>\n        <p>AAW has been designing and building in-ear monitors since 2014 from a single workshop at 76 Playfair Road in Singapore. Every custom is 3D-printed, hand-finished, assembled, and measured under one roof — by people who know each monitor as more than a product. Here is what makes that matter.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"ci-approach-grid\">\n        <div class=\"ci-approach-card\">\n          <h3>Made Under One Roof</h3>\n          <p>Where many brands outsource shell production or driver assembly, AAW controls the full build. Impressions are 3D-scanned on site. Shells are printed in our own lab. Drivers are installed and crossed over by hand. Every pair is measured on an analyser and listened to before it leaves us. When something needs attention, the person who built your monitor is in the same building as the person who cares for it.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ci-approach-card\">\n          <h3>A Decade of Driver Mastery</h3>\n          <p>From the entry-level A3H+ Lux to the flagship Z07 and Canary Pro, AAW has shipped hybrid, tribrid, electrostatic, and all-BA configurations across generations. Our reference Mockingbird is built around a 9-driver hybrid architecture; Canary Pro spans fourteen drivers across a four-way crossover. Every platform is voiced to a coherent target — never to a driver count.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ci-approach-card\">\n          <h3>Voiced by Ear, Validated by Measurement</h3>\n          <p>We tune for musicality first. Every AAW monitor is voiced by hand before it is confirmed on the analyser. The objective is a signature that holds you through hours of listening — never analytical to the point of fatigue, never coloured to the point of dishonesty. Our customs follow the same tuning targets as our universals, so the demo you audition is the sound you receive in your custom build.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"ci-note\" style=\"margin-top:32px;\">\n        <strong>Visit the Workshop</strong>\n        <p>Our showroom at 76 Playfair Road, #01-03 LHK2 Building is open for auditions and impression services. Hear the full AAW lineup side by side, place a custom shell against your own ear, and have your impressions taken by a trained team. <a href=\"/pages/contact\">Book an appointment</a> or walk in during business hours.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n</div>",
        "content_width": "large",
        "text_alignment": "left",
        "color_scheme": "primary",
        "top_space_desktop": 0,
