      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "settings": {
        "section_visibility": "always",
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"ci-feature-shell\">\n  <section class=\"ci-final\">\n    <div class=\"ci-wrap ci-final-inner\">\n      <h2>Your custom is waiting to be built.</h2>\n      <p>Begin with a faceplate. End with an instrument that fits no one else. Browse the AAW custom platforms, place your order, and let our Singapore workshop walk you through impressions, design, and delivery — from the first scan to the first listen.</p>\n      <div class=\"ci-actions\">\n        <a class=\"ci-btn\" href=\"/collections/custom-iem\">Browse Custom IEMs</a>\n        <a class=\"ci-btn secondary\" href=\"/pages/get-started\">How to Order</a>\n        <a class=\"ci-btn secondary\" href=\"/pages/contact\">Contact Us</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n</div>\n<script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\n  \"@graph\": [\n    {\n      \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n      \"@id\": \"https://www.aaw.me/#organization\",\n      \"name\": \"Advanced AcousticWerkes\",\n      \"alternateName\": \"AAW\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.aaw.me/\",\n      \"logo\": {{ 'aaw-logo-white.svg' | asset_url | prepend: 'https:' | json }},\n      \"image\": {{ 'aaw-ins-hero-ciem-2026.jpg' | asset_url | prepend: 'https:' | json }},\n      \"email\": \"support@aaw.me\",\n      \"telephone\": \"+65 8731 5476\",\n      \"address\": {\n        \"@type\": \"PostalAddress\",\n        \"streetAddress\": \"76 Playfair Road, #01-03 LHK2 Building\",\n        \"addressLocality\": \"Singapore\",\n        \"postalCode\": \"367996\",\n        \"addressCountry\": \"SG\"\n      },\n      \"sameAs\": [\n        \"https://www.instagram.com/aaw_sg/\",\n        \"https://www.facebook.com/AdvancedAcousticWerkes/\"\n      ],\n      \"foundingDate\": \"2014\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"@type\": \"WebSite\",\n      \"@id\": \"https://www.aaw.me/#website\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.aaw.me/\",\n      \"name\": \"Advanced AcousticWerkes\",\n      \"publisher\": {\"@id\":