        "section_visibility": "always",
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"ci-feature-shell\">\n  <section class=\"ci-section ci-gallery-section\">\n    <div class=\"ci-wrap\">\n      <div class=\"ci-section-head\">\n        <p class=\"ci-kicker\">Visual Library</p>\n        <h2>Every Build Looks Different Because Every Ear Is Different</h2>\n        <p>Custom monitors are part instrument, part object portrait. These images mix current theme photography with AAW Instagram archive moments: translucent shells, artwork studies, internal driver maps, and finished pairs built for real listeners.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"ci-gallery-grid\" aria-label=\"AAW custom in-ear monitor visual examples\">\n        <figure class=\"ci-gallery-card large\">\n          <img src=\"{{ 'aaw-ins-gallery-custom-2025-900.jpg' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"AAW custom in-ear monitor gallery showing multiple shell colors and faceplate styles\" loading=\"lazy\">\n          <figcaption><span>Instagram archive</span><b>Design Range</b><p>Shell color, faceplate material, artwork, and engraving choices turn the acoustic shell into something personal.</p></figcaption>\n        </figure>\n        <figure class=\"ci-gallery-card tall\">\n          <img src=\"{{ 'aaw-ins-2026-z06-red.jpg' | asset_img_url: '1200x' }}\" alt=\"AAW Z06 custom monitor with crimson resin faceplates and metallic engraving\" loading=\"lazy\">\n          <figcaption><span>Instagram archive</span><b>Z06 Custom Artwork</b><p>Crimson resin and metallic detail show how a custom build can carry a visual signature as clearly as a sonic one.</p></figcaption>\n        </figure>\n        <figure class=\"ci-gallery-card\">\n          <img src=\"{{ 'canary-pro-driver-map.jpg' | asset_img_url: '1200x' }}\" alt=\"Canary Pro custom IEM driver map showing internal acoustic architecture\" loading=\"lazy\">\n          <figcaption><span>Theme asset</span><b>Driver Architecture</b><p>Multi-driver customs are compact acoustic systems, not decorative shells with drivers inside.</p></figcaption>\n        </figure>\n        <figure class=\"ci-gallery-card\">\n          <img src=\"{{ 'ash-custom-blue-gold.jpg' | asset_img_url: '1200x' }}\" alt=\"AAW custom in-ear monitor in blue and gold shell finish\" loading=\"lazy\">\n          <figcaption><span>Theme asset</span><b>Material Finish</b><p>Color depth, flakes, plates, and polishing make the finish readable from across a desk.</p></figcaption>\n        </figure>\n        <figure class=\"ci-gallery-card wide\">\n          <img src=\"{{ 'aaw-ins-method-custom-group-2026-900.jpg' | asset_img_url: '1200x' }}\" alt=\"AAW custom monitor group photo from Instagram-style product photography\" loading=\"lazy\">\n          <figcaption><span>Instagram archive</span><b>Workshop Output</b><p>Every pair starts from an individual impression, then becomes a one-off build in the Singapore workshop.</p></figcaption>\n        </figure>\n        <figure class=\"ci-gallery-card\">\n          <img src=\"{{ 'halcyon-ciem-fit-2.jpg' | asset_img_url: '1200x' }}\" alt=\"AAW custom in-ear monitor worn in ear showing low-profile fit\" loading=\"lazy\">\n          <figcaption><span>Theme asset</span><b>Fit in Use</b><p>The profile follows the ear, distributing weight instead of relying on a compressed ear tip.</p></figcaption>\n        </figure>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n</div>",
